00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:12.300
UM, LISTEN TO THIS.
IF YOU DRIVE A CAR--

00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:14.000
YOU KNOW THE COMMERCIALS ON TV--

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.733
HAVE YOU SEEN FOR THE CARS
THAT BRAKE ON THEIR OWN?

00:00:16.733 --> 00:00:19.533
NOT BREAK, LIKE THEY'RE BROKEN.
BECAUSE...

00:00:19.533 --> 00:00:22.300
BUT, LIKE, BRAKE--THE--
THEY JUST STOP ON THEIR OWN.

00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:23.433
HAVE YOU SEEN THOSE?

00:00:23.433 --> 00:00:25.100
all: YES.
