TO THEIR CARS.

00:00:26.966 --> 00:00:29.833
SO NOW, IF THERE'S SOMETHING
ON THE ROAD THAT YOU DON'T SEE,

00:00:29.833 --> 00:00:31.933
THE CAR JUST STOPS FOR YOU.

00:00:31.933 --> 00:00:32.933
IT'S AMAZING.

00:00:32.933 --> 00:00:36.000
HOPEFULLY.
UM...

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.400
IT'S PRETTY CRAZY THAT
CARS STOP AUTOMATICALLY

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:39.466
