DOES NOT HAVE THAT TECHNOLOGY...

00:00:47.933 --> 00:00:51.166
GET YA IN THE OL' KEESTER,
RIGHT AWAY.

00:00:51.166 --> 00:00:53.333
SO THERE ARE CARS
THAT BRAKE ON THEIR OWN.

00:00:53.333 --> 00:00:55.466
THERE ARE CARS
THAT PARK ON THEIR OWN.

