THAT ACTUALLY CHANGES LANES

00:00:58.766 --> 00:01:01.900
ON ITS OWN WHEN YOU TURN
YOUR TURN SIGNAL ON.

00:01:01.900 --> 00:01:03.166
WHAT HAPPENS WHEN YOU--

00:01:03.166 --> 00:01:06.066
YOU KNOW HOW YOU FORGET
TO TURN IT OFF ACCIDENTALLY?

00:01:06.066 --> 00:01:08.666
JUST END UP GOING IN CIRCLES
OVER AND OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

00:01:08.666 --> 00:01:11.433
"WHAT AM I DOING?
I GOT OFF THE HIGHWAY."

00:01:11.433 --> 00:01:13.233
