THAT DRIVE THEMSELVES.

00:01:13.233 --> 00:01:16.366
BASICALLY THE ONLY THING LEFT
FOR YOU TO DO IS TO--

00:01:16.366 --> 00:01:18.733
WHEN YOU'RE IN YOUR CAR--
LIKE, PUT ON MASCARA AND SMOKE.

00:01:18.733 --> 00:01:20.833
THAT'S ABOUT ALL...

00:01:20.833 --> 00:01:22.066
THIS WILL CHANGE THINGS.

00:01:22.066 --> 00:01:23.633
